    "asOf": "2009-11-04",
    "date": "2009-12-08T16:45:24Z",
    "text": "Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow decedent estates to base the value of qualified historic property on the net earnings of such property for estate and gift tax purposes. Defines \"qualified historic property\" as any building designated as a national historic landmark for at least 25 years prior to the death of a decedent and originally used for residential or farming purposes."
